# Unwind in the blog

Example:

db.posts.aggregate([
	/* unwind by tags */
	{"$unwind" : "$tags"},
	/* now group by tags, counting each tag */
	{"$group:"
	 {"_id":"$tags",
	  "count":{$sum:1}
	 }
	},
	/* sort by popularity */
	{"$sort":{"count":-1}},
	/* show me the top 10 */
	{"$limit" : 10},
	/* change the name of _id to be tag */
	{"$project" :
	 {_id:0,
 	  'tag':'$_id',
	  'count': 1 
	 }
	}
])


Quiz:

Which grouping operator will enable to you to reverse the effects of an unwind?


$sum

$addToSet

(OK) $push

$first

